    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a project or a parts car. The exterior has substantial wear, including deep scratches, several large dents on the passenger side, and significant rust along the wheel wells. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will likely require a major overhaul, and the transmission is slipping between second and third gears. The interior has torn upholstery and a non-functioning climate control system. Sold strictly as-is.",
